        "text": "<p><strong>The Qure Q-Rejuvalight Pro LED Mask</strong> is an at-home LED light therapy device designed to target fine lines, breakouts, and dullness in just one 3-minute treatment.</p><p>This guide will show you exactly how to use it, care for it, and get the best results from your treatments.</p>"
