      "name": "t:sections.n_guide-content-image-block.name",
      "settings": {
        "use_own_file": true,
        "active": false,
        "must_read": false,
        "heading": "Treatment Modes",
        "text": "<h2>Treatment Modes</h2><p>The Q-Rejuvalight Pro Mask has two complete treatment settings: Skin Rejuvenating or Skin Clearing.</p><p>Press the power button once for Skin Rejuvenating mode, or press it twice for Skin Clearing mode.</p>"
      }
    },
    "n_guide_content_zTqxWp": {
      "type": "n_guide-content",
      "name": "t:sections.n_guide-content.name",
      "settings": {
        "use_own_file": true,
        "active": false,
        "must_read": false,
        "heading": "Care & Maintenance",
        "text": "<h2>Care & Maintenance</h2><p>Wipe the mask down after each treatment.</p><p>Spray with our <a href=\"https://qureskincare.com/products/dermal-mist\" title=\"https://qureskincare.com/products/dermal-mist\">Dermal Mist</a> to sanitize and keep the mask clean for your next use.</p><p>When not in use, place your mask in the luxury storage bag provided with your set. Store it in a cool, moisture-free environment.</p>",
        "slides_per_view": ""
      }
    },
    "n_guide_content_mLg4J7": {
      "type": "n_guide-content",
      "name": "t:sections.n_guide-content.name",
      "settings": {
        "use_own_file": true,
        "active": false,
        "must_read": false,
        "heading": "Troubleshooting & Adjustments",
        "text": "<h2>Troubleshooting & Adjustments</h2><p>Having trouble? Don't worry, most issues are quick to solve.</p><h6>Mask not turning on</h6><ul><li>Make sure the device is fully charged (you'll see a blinking light when charging).</li><li>Remove the mask from the charging cable, as the mask cannot be used while plugged in.</li><li>Check that the USB-C charging cable is fully inserted when charging.</li><li>Still nothing? Try a different outlet or charging cable to rule out charging issues.</li></ul><p>[hr]</p><h6>Mask turning off too early</h6><p>The treatment auto-stops after 3 minutes per treatment. If it's stopping earlier, your mask may need a full recharge.</p><p>[hr]</p><h6>Mask not connecting to the app</h6><p>Ensure your phone/tablet's Location Sharing is on. If connectivity issues persist, try closing the app and reopening to reload it.</p>",
        "slides_per_view": ""
      }
    },
    "n_guide_faq_rGxrx9": {
      "type": "n_guide-faq",
      "blocks": {
        "faq_item_bR4tTE": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "When will I see results?",
            "text": "<p>Some people notice a glow after just one use, but visible improvements usually happen after a few weeks of consistent use.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_RmpLrX": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How often should I use the Q-Rejuvalight Pro Mask?",
            "text": "<p>We recommend using it at least 3–5 times per week for best results. Each session only takes 3 minutes.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_K4miU7": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I use it everyday?",
            "text": "<p>Yes, it's safe for daily use. Just stick to one treatment per day.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_gNcaFt": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I use it with my other skincare products?",
            "text": "<p>Yes, but use the mask first on clean, dry skin. You can apply your serums and moisturizers afterward.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_mgTx8f": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Is it okay to use if I’ve had Botox or filler?",
            "text": "<p>It’s best to wait at least a week post-treatment. When in doubt, check with your practitioner.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_FEJRDd": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do I clean the mask?",
            "text": "<p>Use a soft, damp cloth to wipe the surface. Don’t use harsh cleaners or submerge it in water.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_rPNTJK": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How long does it take to charge?",
            "text": "<p>The Q-Rejuvalight Pro LED Mask fully charges in 2.5 hours. A full battery will then delivery 10 complete treatments.</p><p>The light indicator will blink white to signal low battery.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_ask_plate_TeJ9b9": {
